{
  "stem": "21437.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And very often those that waited, they could see that the other one is, you know, really-- you know, can't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So sometimes you gave them two bites of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "People were willing to do this for one another, to give up-- to give up your lifeline, to really, literally lay down your life, for, for even sometimes people that were-- we were all in the same boat, you know?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't have any more or any less.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Although perhaps sometimes those girls that were in the kitchen perhaps occasionally-- they, they worked in the kitchen-- those large camps-- maybe occasionally they have.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had a little bit more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, uh-- So this is how it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And yet, this is what allowed us to go a little bit longer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because somehow you could-- you saw that goodness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You saw that caring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They looked, you know-- sometimes the face was like-- had no expression, no emotion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But sometimes a flick of a wrist, or sometimes a blink of an eye,  you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's-- You know, I went-- it reminds me--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What reminded me of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to go for a checkup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to a doctor for a-- for a checkup that I am supposed to go--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking about myself, now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to go for a checkup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was at-- the doctor was a total stranger.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've never met this doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked me, do you have certain-- does this happen or that happen?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, oh, thank god.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He never-- he never-- you know, it reminded me of this-- that he is a young man who doesn't know me at all.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Doesn't know me from Adam, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
